      <title>巴克莱分析师称，诺和诺德的抛售是过度反应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-20/novo-selloff-is-an-overreaction-barclays-field-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱欧洲制药研究主管艾米丽·菲尔德 (Emily Field) 对诺和诺德股价因实验性减肥药 CagriSema 未能达到预期而遭遇抛售做出了反应。她在“彭博未平仓合约”上发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-20/novo-selloff-is-an-overreaction-barclays-field-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 16:23:12 GMT</pubDate>
